28800:〔Kozue〕“Oh, Sena-shan, you're just jealous because you wanted to win-sies too♪”\p;
28900:〔Sena〕“...Who says I care?”\p;
29000:I doubted Kozupii could be so easily fooled here, given her ability to read everything on someone's mind.\p;
29100:〔Kozue〕“Sena-shan, you alwaaays eat Crunchy-kuns all super-duper excited to see if you're a winner!”\p;
